  <entry>
    <title>安装Hexo常见问题</title>
    <url>/2020/01/14/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Hexo%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="安装Hexo常见问题"><a href="#安装Hexo常见问题" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo常见问题"></a>安装Hexo常见问题</h1><h2 id="1-Git-clone-太慢，并出现错误"><a href="#1-Git-clone-太慢，并出现错误" class="headerlink" title="1. Git clone 太慢，并出现错误"></a>1. Git clone 太慢，并出现错误</h2><p><strong>错误如下</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">RPC failed; curl 18 transfer closed with outstanding read data remaining</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li><p>加大缓存区</p>
  <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#约500M </span><br><span class="line">git config --global http.postBuffer 512000000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>少clone一些，–depth 1</p>
<blockquote>
<p>–depth 1 复制深度为1，就是每个文件只取最近一次提交，不是整个历史版本。 </p>
</blockquote>
  <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;flutter&#x2F;flutter.git --depth 1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>从码云上 clone 【推荐】</p>
<ul>
<li><p><strong>把你需要 clone 的目标在 Github 上复制地址</strong></p>
<p><img src="http://pic.fangxutuwen.com/15790090279075.jpg" alt="">   </p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>打开码云<a href="https://gitee.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">gitee.com</a></strong>, 新建仓库-&gt;从 GitHub 导入</p>
<p><img src="http://pic.fangxutuwen.com/15790112635781.jpg" alt=""></p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>在本地用码云的仓库地址 进行 clone</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="2-NPM-安装出现-WARN-checkPermissions-Missing-write-access-to-usr-local-lib-node-modules"><a href="#2-NPM-安装出现-WARN-checkPermissions-Missing-write-access-to-usr-local-lib-node-modules" class="headerlink" title="2. NPM 安装出现 WARN checkPermissions Missing write access to /usr/local/lib/node_modules"></a>2. NPM 安装出现 WARN checkPermissions Missing write access to /usr/local/lib/node_modules</h2><p>npm install xxx 时，因为没有权限造成的该错误。网上普片的处理方式是在命令前加 <code>sudo</code>,但是这样做并没有解决实际问题。一劳永逸的方法如下：</p>
<ul>
<li>修改npm包所安装目录的权限</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo chown -R $USER &#x2F;usr&#x2F;local然后输入密码就可以了</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>接下来可以进行npm全局包安装</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g bower</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="3-发布时出现-ERROR-Deployer-not-found-git"><a href="#3-发布时出现-ERROR-Deployer-not-found-git" class="headerlink" title="3. 发布时出现 ERROR Deployer not found: git"></a>3. 发布时出现 <code>ERROR Deployer not found: git</code></h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 发布静态网页时</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo d</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 出现如下错误</span><br><span class="line">ERROR Deployer not found: git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在 <code>yourblog-path</code> 目录下<strong>执行如下命令</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --save hexo-deployer-git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
